Ah? Yeon Woo?

5
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:24,980
Why am I getting nervous?

6
00:00:25,460 --> 00:00:25,960
Hel..

7
00:00:25,980 --> 00:00:27,720
Hello..

8
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:31,390
