10
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:34,500
Geez…

11
00:00:35,120 --> 00:00:37,980
Ha… He’s just being himself…

12
00:00:39,440 --> 00:00:40,700
Hmm?

13
00:00:41,700 --> 00:00:42,700
Wha..?

14
00:00:42,980 --> 00:00:44,780
Wha…what’s going on…

15
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,120
Without saying hello…

16
00:00:47,420 --> 00:00:48,680
Haaaa..

17
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:53,380
Argh…what in the…

18
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:56,780
Why did he sit here when he wasn’t going to talk?

19
00:00:56,780 --> 00:00:58,000
This is so awkward.

20
00:00:58,300 --> 00:00:59,040
Ah?

21
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:09,100
Oh gosh!

22
00:01:09,180 --> 00:01:10,560
You scared me

23
