26
00:01:18,940 --> 00:01:19,580
What?

27
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:32,880
But… Why did you ignore my hello?

28
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:34,600
I didn’t see you.

29
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,760
What?

30
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:39,680
Ha.. Alright…

31
00:01:44,140 --> 00:01:47,940
Coincidence,
a knot that gives assurance

32
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:11,960
A Day Before Us

